  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat (400°F).",
    "Thread steak, garlic, and parsley onto skewers, leaving space for even cooking.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, and oregano.",
    "Brush the skewers with the marinade, making sure to coat all surfaces.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes per side, or until the steak reaches 135°F for medium-rare.",
